Pre-Game Insights: Namibia comes into the match with strong recent form, while Oman will be eager to prove their capabilities on the big stage.
Namibia earned their place in the 2024 T20 World Cup with a flawless performance in the Africa Regional Qualifiers, winning all six matches.
Key players like J.P. Kotze and Gerhard Erasmus have shown excellent form with the bat, while Erasmus and Bernard Scholtz have been impressive with the ball.
This combination of strong batting and effective bowling depth gives Namibia an edge over Oman.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The T20 World Cup 2024 will see Namibia face off against Oman on Monday, June 3 2024, at the Kensington Oval, Bridgetown, Barbados.
The toss of the ICC T20 World Cup 2024 match between Namibia and Oman will take place at 05:30 am IST.
According to Dafabet, Namibia are the favorites to win the T20 World Cup 2024 match against Oman.
Others: Predicted XI for Namibia: Jean-Pierre Kotze(WK), Malan Kruger, Jan Frylinck, Gerhard Erasmus(C), David Wiese, Zane Green(WK), JJ Smit, Dylan Leicher, Ruben Trumpelmann, Bernard Scholtz, Tangeni Lungameni
Predicted XI for Oman: Kashyapkumar Prajapati, Mohammed Naseem Kushi(WK), Khalid Kail, Aaqib Ilyas(C), Zeeshan Maqsood, Muhammad Nadeem, Ayan Khan, Rafiullah-M, Kaleemullah, Fayyaz Butt, Bilal-Khan
